00:03:05,300 --> 00:03:06,500
A DECENT JOB,

15
00:03:07,100 --> 00:03:09,600
FRIENDS AND NEIGHBORS
WHO LIKE AND RESPECT HIM.

16
00:03:11,700 --> 00:03:13,000
AND FOR A WHILE THERE,

17
00:03:14,100 --> 00:03:15,600
WITHOUT HARDLY
EVEN REALIZING IT,

18
00:03:17,300 --> 00:03:18,500
I HAD ALL THAT.

19
00:03:20,300 --> 00:03:21,500
I WAS A HAPPY MAN.


