Man: HEY, HANK!

24
00:03:36,500 --> 00:03:38,000
HEY, HAPPY NEW YEAR,
SCHMITT!

25
00:03:41,200 --> 00:03:42,700
HEY, LINDA,
HAPPY NEW YEAR.

26
00:03:42,900 --> 00:03:43,600
HAPPY NEW YEAR.

27
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:45,000
HEY, WHERE YOU
GUYS GOING?

28
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:46,100
SLEDDING! SLEDDING!

29
